# e51ccaa37c254d7d804a8f11ebfbbf7d
msgid "As to why Enterprise Linux specifically is the distribution of choice;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduction/what-is-the-recommended-distribution.rst:152
# 682864777deb4560a7cb05b6956c5209
